OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,8,FStew speaks to three soldiers who have
OL,9,Fall been diagnosed with the same rare
OL,10,Fblood vessel condition in their brains
OL,12,FIn his time as a reservist in the
OL,13,FRoyal Artillery, Steven Cunningham
OL,14,Fserved three full tours of
OL,15,FAfghanistan, crewing a powerful field-
OL,16,Fgun capable of hurling a 35lb shell a
OL,17,Fdistance of 12 miles.
