OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FHe later served as the One O'clock
OL,8,FGunner at Edinburgh Castle, firing a
OL,9,Fblank round from a similar gun every
OL,10,Fsingle day.
OL,12,FResearch suggests the blast
OL,13,Foverpressure from each live round
OL,14,FSteven fired, in training and in war,
OL,15,Fhad a damaging effect on his brain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
