OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FThere is no published science to
OL,8,Fsuggest blank rounds have the same
OL,9,Feffect but it seems possible -
OL,10,FEdinburgh Castle recently moved
OL,11,Fspectators further away from the daily
OL,12,Ffiring due to unspecified "safety
OL,13,Fconcerns" from the MoD.
OL,15,F"You feel like the blast wave," Steven
OL,16,Ftold ITV News. "But you don't really
OL,17,Fpay much attention to it. You just get
OL,18,Fthe rounds down. Everything else is
OL,19,Fout of your head."
