OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FWe know that exposure to blast
OL,8,Fshockwaves can cause brain damage.
OL,9,FScientists believe repeated exposure
OL,10,Fto blasts has long term neurological
OL,11,Fconsequences in some people. But could
OL,12,Fthat repeated exposure also affect the
OL,13,Fblood vessels?
OL,15,FAfter collapsing with a seizure,
OL,16,Fdoctors discovered an arteriovenous
OL,17,Fmalformation (AVM) in Steven's brain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
