OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FIt is an extremely rare condition.
OL,8,FInstead of blood passing slowly from
OL,9,Farteries into veins through a network
OL,10,Fof fine capillaries, he has an
OL,11,Firregular connection formed by a
OL,12,Ftangled mass of blood vessels.
OL,14,FThis abnormal structure operates under
OL,15,Fhigher pressure, meaning the vessels
OL,16,Fcan weaken or even burst ` something
OL,17,Fthat can be fatal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
