OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,F"No, never thought about it," he said.
OL,9,FI then set up a video conference with
OL,10,Ftwo former US Marines who are also
OL,11,Fsuffering from AVMs.
OL,13,FLike Steven, both William Wilcox and
OL,14,FMike Lozano were exposed to shockwaves
OL,15,Ffrom their own weapons. They believe
OL,16,Fthe odds of both developing AVMs
OL,17,Fshortly after leaving the Marines
OL,18,Fcannot be a coincidence.
