OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,F"Essentially, my brain exploded,"
OL,8,FWilliam said. "Mathematically it is
OL,9,Fimpossible for us to both have AVMs,
OL,10,Fdo the same job and know a singular
OL,11,Fperson that we both served with."
OL,13,FSteven listened intently. Descriptions
OL,14,Fof headaches, memory loss and
OL,15,Fdifficulty concentrating mirrored
OL,16,Fexactly how he has been feeling.
