OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FEvidence of a possible link is
OL,8,Fbeginning to emerge. Research in the
OL,9,FUnited States has found that repeated
OL,10,Fexposure to even low-level blasts can
OL,11,Ftrigger AVMs in mice.
OL,13,F"It's clear from the animal studies
OL,14,Fthat there is damage to the blood
OL,15,Fvessels," explained neurologist
OL,16,FProfessor Arshad Majid from the
OL,17,FUniversity of Sheffield.
OL,19,F"We don't have enough information in
OL,20,Fhumans that there is damage to the
OL,21,Fblood vessels, but it's plausible."
