OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,FDr Michael T. Lawton, the surgeon who
OL,8,Foperated on William, believes further
OL,9,Fresearch is urgently needed.
OL,11,F"The shock wave could alter the
OL,12,Fgenetic health of a cell," he told ITV
OL,13,FNews.
OL,15,F"It's just like when you radiate a
OL,16,Fcell and you damage the DNA that might
OL,17,Fdo something to a particular gene's
OL,18,Fability to express itself the same
OL,19,Fcould be true for a blast type injury."
