OL,12,FSteven says his condition has left him
OL,13,Funable to hold down a job. He suffers
OL,14,Fnot only from seizures, but from
OL,15,Fmemory loss and debilitating brain fog.
OL,17,F"I got escorted off the Tay Bridge,"
OL,18,Fhe told me, tears welling in his eyes.
