OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,F"I just felt like I didn't want to be
OL,8,Fhere anymore, it was just... like I
OL,9,Fwish I hadn't come back."
OL,11,FAVMs are often undiagnosed because
OL,12,Ftheir symptoms ` including headaches,
OL,13,Fanxiety, depression and confusion `
OL,14,Fcan be attributed to more common brain
OL,15,Fconditions.
OL,17,F"Do you guys fear that there are a lot
OL,18,Fmore men and women walking around
OL,19,Fright now that could have that ticking
OL,20,Ftime bomb inside their heads?" I asked
OL,21,FMike, William and Steven.
