OL,7,FAll three nodded in unison.
OL,9,F"100%," Mike replied. "And I tell
OL,10,Feveryone; dude go get an MRI, get a
OL,11,Freferral to anybody."
OL,13,FIn a statement, the Ministry of
OL,14,FDefence said: "The health and
OL,15,Fwellbeing of our armed forces is
OL,16,Fcritical and we provide specialist
OL,17,Fmedical treatment for Traumatic Brain
OL,18,FInjuries at the Defence Medical
OL,19,FRehabilitation Centre.
