OL,3,CWhy some soldiers believe their own
OL,4,Cweapons damaged blood vessels in their
OL,5,Cbrain
OL,7,F"We know blast exposure causes
OL,8,Fphysical change or injury in the brain
OL,9,Fthat is only now becoming detectable
OL,10,Fand recognised with recent advances in
OL,11,Fthe field, and we know there are
OL,12,Falleged long-term effects of this
OL,13,Fexposure, but causation has not yet
OL,14,Fbeen shown and is the subject of much
OL,15,Fongoing research".
